                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00 R 296/512: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kellogg</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-08-18T13:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 18, 1924—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>305. I am in entire accord with your point of view. I think Owen Young’s
                    appointment is highly desirable if it can be effected.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
